      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p><em>Lands beyond Hadrian's Wall. Never truly conquered by Rome. Picts, wild tribes, savage barbarians (by Roman view). Contains tribes: Otadini, Damnonii, Novantae, Selgovae, Votadini. Remote, dangerous, less explored.</em></p><p><em>Refer to the Britannia & Beyond rulebook for full details.</em></p>",
